longBusinessSummary: Sporttotal AG produces, broadcasts, and markets sports and adventure events worldwide. It also offers technical equipment of racetracks, as well as sports and meeting places. The company was formerly known as _wige MEDIA AG and changed its name to Sporttotal AG in September 2017. Sporttotal AG was founded in 1978 and is based in Cologne, Germany.
